<MEMO>  People.
Compiled from Mercury News wire services.  </MEMO>
<TEXT>     (check) Bruce Springsteen still faces that lawsuit by two former assistants
who contend he owes them overtime pay from his 1984-'85 "Born in the U.S.A."
tour. He is countersuing one of them, saying that he took tapes and other
property.  </TEXT>
